@startuml
title Authentication Credentials - Activity Diagram

start

:Open Login Page;
note right
User opens the login interface.
end note

:Enter Credentials;
note right
Student enters username and password.
end note

:Submit Login;
note right
Student submits the login form.
end note

:Authenticate User;
note right
Login UI sends username and password to AuthController.
end note

:Verify Credentials;
note right
AuthController checks credentials with UserAccount.
end note

if (Credentials Valid?) then (Yes)
  :Return Status (Success);
  note right
  System returns successful authentication result.
  end note
else (No)
  :Return Status (Failure);
  note right
  System returns failed authentication result.
  end note
endif

:Display Login Result;
note right
Login UI displays success or error message to the student.
end note

stop
@enduml
